{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this [? shouldn't ?] kill him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he ran away, without nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I saw what is.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the morning, they put us on some barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the morning, we woke up-- [GERMAN]! 'Out, out!' They are going, 'Out, [GERMAN] appel.' [GERMAN] appel meant the counting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You had to stay in the line, five in a row.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this is the way they are going to count them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- you should freeze to death, because it was Christmas.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was cold, horribly cold, punishable cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They took pails of cold water, and they was just shooting over your head, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You should freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was a very nice, sunny day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was at Christmas Day, December the 25th, 1944.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- the head Gestapo is coming out, and the other Gestapo-- he says, 'Hansel!' [? 'Ja.' ?] On the railway tracks, there were frozen, naked bodies-- but skeletons, of course.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He starts-- the head Gestapo starts laughing like a horse. 'Ha ha, ha ha, ha ha!' 'Hansel, [GERMAN].' 'Hansel, what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are you making here a beach?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are tanning themselves on the sun on the beach [INAUDIBLE].' When I saw that, I said to myself, 'How long is it going to take until I am going to look the same?'",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Here, they took us out to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, they brought in-- what-- we were digging trenches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really, they didn't need the trenches, because here, they didn't have a chance that they should be against Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Russia was pushing when they were pushing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't [? look ?] at nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything what had-- it had a goal.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
